<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Greenview</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Homes for sale in Greenview comprise an eclectic mix of housing options ranging from two-storey homes, to split level units, bungalows, townhouses, duplexes and even condominiums that are readily available at an average price of $250,000. </p>
            <p class="par-xl">Initially a part of the Thorncliffe/Greenview neighborhood, the community got separated in 1991 and is now among the most desirable in the entire city.</p>
        </div>
